      "heading": null,
      "description": "Whisk the tahini with the water until creamy, then set aside."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Mince the ginger. Roughly chop the tomatoes and finely slice the spring onion."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add the vegan butter to a small frying pan set over a medium heat. Once the butter has melted, add the nuts and/or seeds and cook for 5 mins, stirring often, until toasted. Add the ginger and sugar and stir for 1 min, then remove from the heat. Add the chilli flakes, soy sauce and the juice of half the lime. Stir to combine."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
